Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:21.90,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(130,130)}守电话·宣布紧急事态
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.68,0:24:14.83,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 台风过后·虚像与实像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:16.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尿出来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:31.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「司…令部直…通高…度紧…急非…常事\N…态用指…令传…达线…路维…护确…认任…务」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这名堂真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:36.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是非常重要的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.47,0:02:40.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是失败了 可能小队全员都会受到惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:48.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据情况 有可能发起第一警戒态势\N给这区域的所有分队下达紧急出动准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:53.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊对啊 责任非常重大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:57.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么样的任务呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:58.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:02.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守电话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:11.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这电话是连接首都的热线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:13.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它有响过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:14.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:16.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:24.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 虽然响了就麻烦\N但如果在真正需要的时候不响的话 会更麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:28.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以半年一度 确认线路是否连通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:29.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司…司…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 好好记住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:37.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「司令部直通非常紧急…」 诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:42.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 是「司令部直通高度非常事…」 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:49.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「司令部直通高度紧急非常事态用指令传达线路维护确认任务」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:50.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:55.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做我做我要做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:58.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我做那个任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:01.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很想通一通电话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:03.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要这么兴奋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:07.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本构造是跟建御雷神的内部通话一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是距离离得远点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:11.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:14.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然可以跟距离很远的人说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:15.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:21.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 的确跟完全见不到面的人说话 感觉不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:24.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 弄熟了就觉得没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:28.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有个麻烦 不知道今天什么时候打过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:30.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样你也愿意做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:31.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:36.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那你今天整天守着电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:42.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呤呤呤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:49.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是赫尔维西亚陆军第1121号要塞 空深彼方二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:56.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 听完电话了就把它放回原位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:57.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲…菲莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:42.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:44.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉西娅姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:48.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得都觉得闷热
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:51.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火车？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:55.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必须尽快送到司令部的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:58.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯下个星期来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要去车站
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:03.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你好好守电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:04.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:05.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一有什么差错的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:10.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟糕的情况 有可能会被认为这里受到攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:11.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好守住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:36.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:37.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全没睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有见到乃绘留了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:47.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:49.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在机库吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:51.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:54.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方 中午想吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:59.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气 今天是我值日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:00.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:07.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你和暮羽为什么一到我值日做饭的时候 什么都不让我做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:11.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来之前 我也做得不少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:13.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道也应该不差的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:19.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确味道没有外观那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:21.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:24.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 味道鲜明 很美的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:30.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 那今天就比平时更卖力地做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:34.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:34.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:37.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 是直美姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:41.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:45.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我要守着电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:47.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:50.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:53.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:01.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混砧板渣的三文治 我可不想再吃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:06.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们喝吧 是苹果汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:12.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是给我们批发苹果汁的农家自制的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:17.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这些跟我们的卡巴度斯是亲戚咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 已经露馅了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:31.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当礼物的两瓶就够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:35.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:38.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有城镇的工商会的集会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:43.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们受他们各方面的通融 按照惯例也得给他们点礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:44.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:45.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:50.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 她们一直都拼命瞒着的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:54.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会露馅的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:56.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:08:57.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:01.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会再给你说明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:06.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个 直美姐也一起吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:10.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 要我也去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:13.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 登在这星期报纸上的新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:17.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎大家都想听听军方的正式说明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:18.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:22.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说休战协定的会议进展不顺的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:23.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:28.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把赔款额和领土划分什么的一一决定好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖延是正常的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:37.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过嘛 工会那些大叔的目的其实也就是想见见你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:41.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说你在泼水节上当炎之少女后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉丝就多了起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦死了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:52.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 貌似我不得不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:56.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身心也早已经是要塞少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人也能完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:00.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:01.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方 给你这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:11.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的旧书 有点过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:15.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是小号的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:20.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了太美了太美了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的喇叭也变得象样起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:26.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是奖励你认真练习的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:30.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有了这书 你也不会犯瞌睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 这就是C
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:44.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D E F G
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:47.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天也要结束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:16.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乃 在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:35.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了 晾的衣服要湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里院属于作战活动范围
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:52.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方 来玩吧{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行不需要检查时间轴 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:58.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方 来玩吧{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:12:00.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:12.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:16.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 晾的衣服没湿真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:17.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:22.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起 突然要您帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:27.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意 我们才是 突然造访真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:32.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就得回到托雷兹 我是来道别的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真客气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:37.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不用给当兵的道别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:40.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能这样说话啊 诚也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:45.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子好像也对你们各位做过不礼貌的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:49.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天也是想来道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:51.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他几位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:53.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:57.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫梨旺小姐吗 那位黑发的小姐也不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:57.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:01.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 可以的话真想见上一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:05.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本书是你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:06.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:10.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小号的书 是梨旺前辈给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:13.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:18.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没没 失礼了 我自言自语
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:21.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方一个人看家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:32.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部直通高度紧急非常事态用指令传达线路维护确认任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:33.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…执行中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:40.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 是在等这个响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:41.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:46.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我是第一次用 有点紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:50.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己能不能好好说话呢…什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要练习一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:14:00.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 由美奈也去参加工会集会了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:06.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她去取工会各位的捐赠物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:07.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 请喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:15.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 诚也也快喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:19.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然喝 不过别以为这就拉拢到我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:27.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:31.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美汐你们看得出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:33.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:43.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的就是电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:45.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:50.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们喜欢 我偶尔会做给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:51.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 诚也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:55.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:02.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:04.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 好厉害啊 诚也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:06.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得很清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 一开始要说「喂」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:10.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是打电话的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:15.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:20.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 真的 真的能听到声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个练习就好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:23.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:26.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:27.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:36.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是赫尔维西亚陆军第1121号要塞 空深彼方二等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:38.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:41.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦您专程打来电话 在下感到惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:43.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:46.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:47.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 小鸟先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美汐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:50.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:51.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:56.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:10.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:33.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 祭司爷爷和我们那里的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:55.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:00.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸神们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:06.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等失态 不是来表示一直以来的感谢和歉意的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然玩猎奇起来 还给人家添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:12.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们今晚没饭吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:13.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:15.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没得吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:23.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没问题了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你衣服也湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 还有换的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有妙计
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:43.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这衣服…羞死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:44.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么的华丽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:52.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 谢谢你 由美奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这衣服我会洗好再还你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:56.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 送给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对孩子们来说太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:04.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不会有其他人比彼方更适合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:08.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次还能陪我们玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚也下次也要来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:15.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时间我再来陪你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:30.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们告辞了 愿您们万福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:34.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感…感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:41.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 要收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:45.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚忘了 上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:21.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人…快点来…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:17.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那群大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:26.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 彼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前…辈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:32.91,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 请救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…怎么了 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:37.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:41.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快尿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:44.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去 会憋出病的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:46.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:49.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直憋着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:52.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道说她耿直还是敦实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:01.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:04.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:06.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.38,0:21:10.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 我已经一步也动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:14.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个没时运的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:22.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是赫尔维西亚陆军第1121小队 梨旺·和宫军士长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:29.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违了 听说要跟你们那边确认线路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:30.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就请求…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:32.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要逃避吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:34.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 我没有逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:39.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 你只是没有原谅我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:43.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你还找我什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:47.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 拯救这个国家 拯救赫尔维西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:52.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:57.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乃 难道你一直…从早上开始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:22:00.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在厕所很好睡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:02.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.52,0:22:07.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来…哇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:10.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么穿得这么可爱啊 小彼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:14.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你们两个在走廊干什么啊
